<p>From the airport, we can be reached by Croatia Airlines Shuttles, which are driving to the central bus terminal. The ticket is HRK 30,- (&euro; 4,- / $ 6,-). The drive from the airport to the central bus terminal takes about thirty minutes. The first shuttle leaves the airport at 05:00 AM; the last at 20:00. After 20:00 the shuttle leave airport after every regular Croatia Airlines landing. From the bus terminal to the apartment You can get as described above.</p>

