<h3>From the central bus terminal</h3>

<p>You can reach us straight from Autobusni kolodvor (Central Bus Station) on Držićeva Street by tram line number 5, direction Prečko. You get off at Vrbik stop and from there it&rsquo;ll take you around 5 minutes on foot walking down the Fausta Vrančića and II Vrbik streets.</p>

<h3>From the main train station</h3>

<p>The fastest way to reach us from the central railway station is on foot. Descend down the staircase of the Importane Centar passage and walk to Vukovarska Avenue, then down the avenue to Vrbik tram stop, and then down Faust Vrančić Street to II Vrbik Street. The walk lasts for approximately 15 minutes. If you want, you can go by tram, riding the line number 4, direction Savski most. You get off at \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\&quot;Učiteljski fakultet\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\&quot; stop and from there it&#39;ll take you around 5 minutes on foot walking in the direction of the Kninski trg. (see map)</p>

<h3>From the airport</h3>

<p>The Croatia Airlines offer a shuttle-bus service to the Central Bus Station (Autobusni kolodvor). One-way ticket costs HRK 30. The ride lasts around half an hour. The shuttle-bus leaves in front of the main airport entrance every 30 minutes. The first one leaves at 05:00 hrs, while the last one leaves at 20:00 hrs. After that, the bus leaves upon regular landings of Croatia Airlines&rsquo; airplanes. To reach the apartment from the Central Bus Station just follow the above mentioned instructions. For other details please follow the link: <a href=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\&quot;\\&quot;\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\&quot;\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\&quot;http://www.plesoprijevoz.hr\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\&quot;\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\&quot;\\&quot;\\&quot;\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\">plesoprijevoz.hr</a> (in Croatian or English)</p>

<h3>By taxi</h3>

<p>If you&#39;re reaching us by taxi, just memorise the address &ndash; II Vrbik 14. Taxi stands can be found in front of both the central bus and railway stations, and in front of the main entrance to the airport.</p>

